title: Red Hat Enterprise AS4: 6.out Killed
body:
by **Ziyu4Huang**: 
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. 6g  hello.go; 6l hello.go
2. 6.out

What is the expected output? What do you see instead?
executable just throws "Killed" message

What is your $GOOS?  $GOARCH?
linux
amd64

Which revision are you using?  (hg identify)
Rev 3160c0fad7

Please provide any additional information below.
It can work with 386, but not amd64

System detail:
cat /etc/redhat-release
Red Hat Enterprise Linux AS release 4 (Nahant Update 6)

The spec of the machine is .
AS4 (64-bit)    2.6.9-67.ELsmp  IntXeon 2.93G, RAM72G
